{
  "chapter": 30,
  "chapter_summary": "方宝玉被埋于地下，偷听蒙面人与冷冰鱼密谋以武林盟主之位利诱结盟。魏不贪被收买后暗杀师弟杨不怒，伪造证据嫁祸方宝玉。群豪发现尸体后果然中计，暴雨救了一息尚存的宝玉。七大弟子连遭不幸，莫不屈、公孙不智、石不为讨论案情，公孙不智推断凶手是熟人，怀疑魏不贪。魏不贪假装中毒以消除嫌疑，趁公孙不智救他时暗施毒手，公孙不智中暗器后失踪。泰山竞技大会前夕群雄汇聚，方宝玉下落不明、被诬为杀人凶手的消息传开。棺材中藏着一位神秘白发老人。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "text": "此地绝无人来打扰，你我正好谈话。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "冷冰鱼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既有机密之事与我相商，便该与我坦诚相见才是，为何还要如此藏头露尾，又蒙住了面目。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "text": "你若是相信于我，不瞧我面目又有何妨？\n你若是根本不相信我，瞧见我面目也是无用的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "冷冰鱼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，有什么话？你只管说吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "text": "此番泰山较技之会，阁下若能技冠群雄，便不啻登上当今天下武林盟主的宝座，不知阁下是否有意？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "冷冰鱼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个冷某自然早已知道，难道你此刻说了这番话后，冷某便能登上那武林盟主的宝座不成？\n你说了又有何用？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "text": "自然有用的。我且问你，此番泰山会中，武功真能威胁于你的对手，除了方宝玉与七大弟子外，还有什么人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "冷冰鱼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "七大弟子也未必是冷某的对手……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "冷冰鱼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除了他们外，别的，冷某更未放在眼中。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "text": "这就是了。我若能令这些人全都无法去泰山与你交手，你岂非便可稳稳登上那武林盟主的宝座？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "冷冰鱼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我与你素不相识，你为何要如此相助于我？\n你究竟有何企图？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "text": "若无我相助，你万难登上武林盟主的宝座，这点想必你自己也清楚得很。\n你登上盟主宝座后，想必定不会忘了我的好处，而我，也不愿出面去争那盟主之位，是以你我合则两利，分则两败。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "冷冰鱼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你要我怎样？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "text": "只要你写下字据，与我订下同盟之后，奉我如兄，终身不得违背，我便可一手将你扶上宝座了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "冷冰鱼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你虽说得如此确定，但我又怎能信得过你？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "text": "你立刻便可信得过了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "text": "藏起身形……快！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_bu_nu",
      "speaker_name": "杨不怒",
      "listener": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "text": "你说要去责骂宝儿，却为何将我带来这里？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "speaker_name": "魏不贪",
      "listener": "char_yang_bu_nu",
      "text": "但我总得先问问你，为何对宝玉如此气恼？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_bu_nu",
      "speaker_name": "杨不怒",
      "listener": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "text": "宝儿这孩子，近来行事之乖僻可恨，委实令人无法想象。\n就以方才来说，他明明早已来到这里，却偏偏要等到我丢人现眼之时才肯现身，才肯出手，这是为了什么，我好歹也得问个清楚！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "speaker_name": "魏不贪",
      "listener": "char_yang_bu_nu",
      "text": "你方才为何不问？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_bu_nu",
      "speaker_name": "杨不怒",
      "listener": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "text": "他战胜之后，根本未将我瞧在眼里，全不过来与我相见！\n不错，那时是有些人在围住他，但他难道不会推开那些人么？\n我越想越觉气恼，一怒之下，便索性走了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "speaker_name": "魏不贪",
      "listener": "char_yang_bu_nu",
      "text": "如今你想怎样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_bu_nu",
      "speaker_name": "杨不怒",
      "listener": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "text": "你既已星夜赶回，自当去问问他，为何要如此对我？\n这些天他究竟去了哪里……？他……他究竟在搞什么鬼？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "speaker_name": "魏不贪",
      "listener": "char_yang_bu_nu",
      "text": "这其中秘密，只怕你永远都不会知道了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_bu_nu",
      "speaker_name": "杨不怒",
      "listener": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "text": "我为何永远不会知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "speaker_name": "魏不贪",
      "listener": "char_yang_bu_nu",
      "text": "那是什么人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_bu_nu",
      "speaker_name": "杨不怒",
      "listener": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "text": "那有什么……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "speaker_name": "魏不贪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老七，你莫要怪我，我不得不如此。\n你若觉黄泉路上太过寂寞，我立刻就会找人来陪你的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "speaker_name": "魏不贪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方宝玉……方宝玉……此番你又惨了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "text": "魏老五，你干得好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "speaker_name": "魏不贪",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "这点小事算什么？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "text": "你只要如此干下去，你所梦想的一切，便都会得到的，我担保可以让你得到世上最大的财富。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "speaker_name": "魏不贪",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "我也可以向你担保，那几人的性命全包在我手上。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "text": "好……好，你去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "text": "冷少庄主，方才的事，你都已亲眼瞧见了，你觉怎样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "冷冰鱼",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "text": "你此刻是否已相信了我的话？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "冷冰鱼",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "知道了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "text": "这里有三份盟约，只要你写上名字，画上花押，你我便是生死与共、富贵共享的盟友了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "冷冰鱼",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "但……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "text": "良机不再，错过难逢，你还犹豫什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_bing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "冷冰鱼",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "好！\n一言为定，祸福同……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xing_shou",
      "speaker_name": "齐星寿",
      "listener": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "text": "魏兄怎知杨七侠到这里来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "speaker_name": "魏不贪",
      "listener": "char_qi_xing_shou",
      "text": "老七方才已与我见过一面，说要将宝儿带来这里教训一番，问他为何目无尊长……唉！\n老七素来脾气暴躁，而宝儿么……唉！宝儿少年成名，委实也太不将我辈瞧在眼里，我生怕他们言语冲突起来，不可收拾，是以才将各位请来，打个圆场。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xing_shou",
      "speaker_name": "齐星寿",
      "listener": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "text": "这样的和事佬，在下一向最愿当的了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pan_ji_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "潘济城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这里如此静寂，哪有人影？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xing_shou",
      "speaker_name": "齐星寿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们找找……老七……老七，宝儿，你们在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_hu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "惊呼者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好了，这……这……这……杨……杨……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xing_shou",
      "speaker_name": "齐星寿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这是怎么回事？杨七侠遭了谁的毒手？\n方少侠又到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "有人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里有个字……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "有人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "宝！\n是个‘宝’字，杨七侠临死前还写下这‘宝’字，为的是什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pan_ji_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "潘济城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非是……莫非是方少侠……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "speaker_name": "魏不贪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "宝玉！方宝玉！一定是方宝玉下的毒手。\n否则老七又怎会毫无防备，否则普天下又有谁能将咱们老七一掌击毙？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不想方宝玉竟会如此狠毒！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "speaker_name": "魏不贪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位一定要帮我寻着这卑鄙无耻的恶徒。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对！咱们可也不能再容这恶徒活在世上，咱们一定得将他找出来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此暴风雨，咱们还是莫要再找了。方宝玉可非呆子，他杀了人后，还不快快逃走，在这里等死不成？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说得有理，咱们走吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "text": "杨七弟重伤不治在先，金老二饮酒中毒在后，昨夜西门六弟竟又被人暗算，连中三种绝毒暗器，眼见也是活不成了。\n想起我弟兄八人，同投白恩师门下时也有生死与共之誓言，而如今……唉……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我活下去，只为复仇……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "复仇……不错，复仇！但纵算杨七弟是死在宝儿手下，难道老二、老六也是被宝儿害死的么？\n你我连仇人是谁都不知道，还谈什么复仇？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "text": "听你言下之意，老二、老六之死，是断然与方宝玉无关的了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "嗯！不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "text": "但除了方宝玉之外，又有谁会暗算他们？\n又有谁能暗算他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "你必须注意一点：他三人被害后，都毫无挣扎之迹留下，显见是事先毫无防备。\n由此可见，动手加害他们的，必定是他们极为熟悉的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "text": "是以我才算定是方宝玉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "但宝儿害了杨七弟后，老二、老六早已将他视如蛇蝎，只要一见他们，必定叱骂争打起来，怎会那般安静？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "text": "此人既非宝儿，却又是你我十分熟悉的人，那么，他会是谁呢？\n难道是……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "大哥你不妨想一想，你我兄弟间，有谁最易被利诱，老二、老七他们死后，又是谁最先发现的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "text": "你莫非是说魏五弟？\n你怎可如此怀疑于他？你……你……你切莫忘了，他也是你我亲如骨血的兄弟。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "事已至此，你我必须对任何人都要怀疑，宁严不漏，宁枉勿纵……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对！我去瞧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "四弟行事最是沉着谨慎，有他去瞧，错不了的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好，老五莫非也中了毒？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "茶中有毒。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_wei_bu_tan",
      "text": "老五，咱们险些冤枉了你……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我方才确是冤枉了他……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "text": "他……他已无救了么？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "幸好咱们及时发觉，他毒性还未攻心，只要再迟半个时辰，老五这条命便又要真的断送了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "text": "如此说来，他……莫非还有救？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "无妨了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "老五危险已过，有我在这里照料已足够了，四弟你还是陪大哥过去歇歇吧。\n会战之期将至，大哥是万万不可太过劳累的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两人真有福气。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方才是谁在惊呼？公孙二弟哪里去了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方才房中究竟发生了什么事？\n你们可知道？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zu_lin",
      "speaker_name": "金祖林",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞧！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非公孙二弟也中了暗算？此刻竟负伤去追查敌踪去了？\n但……但他为何不通知你我一声，他！他……他怎可孤身涉险？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "潘济城，那随着齐星寿同立、面容惨白、长身玉立的少年人便是五年前怒斩‘快刀手’的潘济城。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是他？就是他！嘿！倒真瞧不出来，这看来有如花花公子般的少年，竟就是江湖传说动手间最冷静的潘济城。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "闻道‘天刀’梅谦此次早已随万子良与七大弟子来到山下，怎的他们直到此刻还不上来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这必是为了七大弟子此刻已只能称为两大弟子了，而且瞧莫不屈的模样，此次已万万不能出手，只怕也不堪一击。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "出道时曾经轰轰烈烈的七大弟子，如今竟落到这样的地步，倒真是令人想不到的事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪的是……他怎的也还未来？听人传言，他仍是此次盛会中夺标希望最大的一人。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天上飞花冷冰鱼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他？怎会是他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嘿嘿！这消息来源机密无比，我虽不能告诉你，却可断定这是万万不会错的，你且等着瞧吧！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但方宝玉……方宝玉又如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方宝玉……哼哼！他只怕永远也无法在人前现身了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_jin_pao_da_han",
      "text": "此地上来虽然困难，但只要一上来，便可安安心心地观战了。\n棺材虽不祥，但坐在上面却舒服得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_pao_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "锦袍大汉",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_da_han",
      "text": "不错，此地纵观战局，确可一目了然……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "棺……棺材里的是什么人？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "棺材装死人，活人离远些。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你究竟是人是鬼？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_da_han",
      "text": "你且莫管我是人是鬼，只要敢再坐在这棺材上，便再也休想活着下山，不信，你两人尽管试试。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我老人家舒舒服服地躺在这里瞧热闹，你两人却要来坐我老人家头上，岂非自找霉气么？\n若非我老人家此刻还不愿现身，你两人此刻哪里还有命在？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 604
    }
  ],
